biography: Martin is a highly accomplished golfer who has made a name for himself on the competitive circuit.  A member of St. Laurence Golf, Martin consistently demonstrates skill and precision on the course.

Martin’s dedication to the game is evident in his impressive track record at the prestigious Hector Trophée.  He boasts an impressive history of appearances, having competed in the tournament in 2022, 2023, 2024, and 2025.  This consistent participation showcases his commitment to excellence and his ambition to succeed at the highest level.

His achievements extend beyond mere participation.  Martin’s strategic prowess and exceptional putting have led him to victory at the Hector Trophée in 2020.  Furthermore, Martin has also claimed the coveted Victor trophy, an individual accolade for the tournament’s top player, in Hector Trophée VI.
